These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, turkish
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, marigold
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the turkish##1
2. the turkish is the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Beverage      | tea     | hot-chocolate |
| Nationality   | turkish | egyptian      |
| Flower         | marigold    | amaryllis      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, singing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, martial-arts
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, chestnut
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |
| Hobby         | singing      | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | adventure    |
| Color           | chestnut         | fuchsia         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, country
2 different pets are kept: mouse, pony
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the fan of rock is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2      |
| Music-Genre         | rock | country |
| Pet         | pony       | mouse       |
| Transport   | tram       | bus         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-4::.
