The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse
1. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Flower   | aconite | lily   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b          | gospel   |
| Sport         | climbing     | lacrosse |

 